                "content": "J'zargo is a confident Khajiit student at the College of Winterhold who fancies himself the best mage among the apprentices. He experiments with lightning-based scrolls and is one of three students who may become a follower.",
                "display_name": "J'zargo - Apprentice",
                "emotion": "",
